          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="ap-frw-footer">
          <button class="ap-frw-back-btn" id="apFrwStep4Back">← Back</button>
          <button class="ap-frw-next-btn" id="apFrwStep4Next">Continue — Display Settings →</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 5: Display Settings -->
      <div id="apFrwStep5" class="ap-frw-step-content" style="display:none;">
        <div class="ap-frw-body">
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(17,16,14,.62);margin:0 0 18px;line-height:1.65;"><strong style="color:#11100e;">Transparency drives sales.</strong> Stores that show their fundraiser progress publicly see significantly more purchases — supporters want to see the goal hit.</p>

          <div class="ap-frw-toggle-row selected" id="apFrwVisRow1" data-val="public">
